name: Xenon Pay
additional_notices: Kindly be aware that liquidity provided in Automated Market Maker platforms (eg. Uniswap, Sushiswap, Balancer) can be removed (also known as rug pulling), resulting in a collapse of available liquidity. Please exercise caution when trading! This notice is NOT directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder for our users.

description.en: X2P (a BSC project) is a frictionless, high-yield, deflationary & decentralized token on the Binance Smart Chain. A 10% transaction fee will be distributed over all X2P holders every time there's a transaction & 5% will go to the Liquidity Pool. Our goal is to motivate people by holding their coins and maximize their profits by doing this. Our system is built so it fits holders and demotivates quick profit (scalping etc.)because of the total 15% transaction fee. Our Tokenomics are designed to be a passive way of staking to long term investors since their tokens will increase with every transaction. Stay with us for the long ride!
